{"tid":1426500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港示威持續內地客憂安危 導遊總工會稱 8 月「零大陸團」","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:56.000Z","uid":1121,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf123757532fd7f5963ae57e87e8f5ea8069c44e","tid":1426500,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"反對逃犯條例條訂引發出一連串示威活動，至今歷時已超過兩個月。不少內地人亦覺得香港已陷入混亂狀態，訪港的意欲似乎大減，好些內地旅行社更索性停辦所有香港旅遊團。香港導遊總工會亦指，8 月份已無內地旅行團訪港。<br />\n<br />\n香港示威活動持續多時，多個國家亦對香港發出旅遊警示，訪港旅客數字升幅放緩。香港導遊總工會表示，8 月份已無正規內地旅行團訪港，只有少量少量承包團，工會所有導遊幾乎零收入。香港入境旅遊接待協會亦指出，假如示威持續發生，旅行社或會出現裁員和減薪潮。<br />\n<br />\n工會又指出，內地部份旅行社亦對此感到憂心，因為保險承包範圍通常不包括暴動及天災人禍等事件，一旦出事有可能要賠償天價數字。"},{"pid":"b9c7e12327656cba7097ec78fc7cbfbe38a20745","tid":1426500,"uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/58356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F58356.jpg&h=c52f6aa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a780930f299a3a0835e650d2834ad941bdc41e0","tid":1426500,"uid":276166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"係銅鑼灣一樣仲見到有大陸人出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bece770e3f18fc477303078103f8ddc777d6cef7","tid":1426500,"uid":5267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c102fa47260fef512b7d71bb4e94aa7f9f34ee2","tid":1426500,"uid":42986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"D導遊咪又係大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd3a3bc5dc071f328385500eecb864ad47c036b","tid":1426500,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bece770e3f18fc477303078103f8ddc777d6cef7","tid":1426500,"uid":5267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"8 月份已無正規內地旅行團訪港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係果班唔正規<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7201e4560afd9551cc4789689935ddc264121376","tid":1426500,"uid":193196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"咪幾好，milestone completed."},{"pid":"c870823739937d060a6814717f325e454d1d3ea7","tid":1426500,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"早啲反抗咪冇囉，去到依家存亡之秋先冇"},{"pid":"00c05f148abb786cd3aa177c132459b5914f4c3e","tid":1426500,"uid":81449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"走粉走水貨果班又咪係自由行"},{"pid":"9b2a9b9b8240ca96bae1c2818a32fdb7b78b56ca","tid":1426500,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"琴日仲見到土瓜灣碼頭大把大陸團上船"}]}